Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.44,0:00:17.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}微风轻吻着脸庞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.55,0:00:20.48,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}用着一种怀念的温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.82,0:00:29.25,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}吹干流下的泪珠轻拂而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.62,0:00:39.43,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是谁 对未来都着着一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:47.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝着明天大步迈进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.07,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.11,0:00:57.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}总有一天会觉醒的 真实心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.89,0:01:03.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}现在就伸出双手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.06,0:01:13.90,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在这开始变化的世界 立刻前往探寻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.17,0:01:19.84,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牵系着你的手绝不再分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.78,0:01:22.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因为有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.08,0:01:27.52,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找寻的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.02,0:01:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第九话  唯你让我心动」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.29,0:01:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是善行忠孝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.46,0:01:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为5121部队的司令官 也担任班上的班长一职
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.90,0:01:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本职务需要沉着冷静的决策力 以及迅速的执行能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.14,0:01:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以必须要将其铭记于心 务必完成达到这样的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.38,0:01:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我的任何判断 都将左右部下们珍贵的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.38,0:02:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.55,0:02:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下会比较有效率的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.12,0:02:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂圭吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.86,0:02:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然被称为含着金汤匙出生 可说是贵族世家的后继者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却自愿入伍服役
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个有能力且冷静的左右手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.71,0:02:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 请等一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.74,0:02:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宫康光、来须银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.35,0:02:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们负责随队步兵的工作 也是HWT驾驶员训练教官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.85,0:02:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于职务有着热情跟矜持 可说是非常难得的人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.76,0:02:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托不要把这个飞车吃掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.13,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是原素子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.66,0:02:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把怪人集结的5121部队比喻成一个猴子军团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么猴老大就是司令官善行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而统管娘子军的母猴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.77,0:03:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更正 美丽的领袖就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.78,0:03:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是在学谁说话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.28,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以叫做娘子军 是因为整备小组只有女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于人手不足 通宵作业是家常便饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机油或化学药物的使用也是肌肤的大敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原学姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要休息一下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.27,0:03:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的点心是苹果派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好吃喔～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.41,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.74,0:03:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森精华
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.14,0:03:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像小狗般粘着我的可爱学妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.75,0:03:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.88,0:03:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是本日派遣到5121部队整备小组的森精华
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫原素子 请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要请您多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不擅长跟人往来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.77,0:04:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢机械！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.04,0:04:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.07,0:04:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只要注入爱情 机械就一定会回报你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.88,0:04:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我喜欢机械 也喜欢人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.39,0:04:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.39,0:04:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边真纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.33,0:04:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生在不幸之星 5121部队的不幸少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.47,0:04:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次去神社抽签 只知道大凶内容为何的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边好慢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今天入队的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是早就要到了才对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起、对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.49,0:04:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起、对不起、对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边怎么了 刚刚怎么好大一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.27,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在小道市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.94,0:05:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于我搭的电车出事 很抱歉会晚点抵达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你自己没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.71,0:05:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是的 托您的福\N-糟糕 那是汽油车啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.39,0:05:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边怎么了？田边？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.23,0:05:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到两个月之后 她才来到了5121部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢苹果的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 好像很好吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂上久臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.11,0:05:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然平常吊儿郎当 但军中经历却是无法想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.68,0:05:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被认为是高深莫测的一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳野春香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.42,0:06:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们班担任一般科目的导师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.06,0:06:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于她的个性 大家都直接叫她春香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都看不出比我们大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.83,0:06:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户口隆之、泷川阳平 他们是HWT的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.14,0:06:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.71,0:06:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从经理、总务到杂用一手包办 自称万能的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是熊本出生 但说话却是关西腔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一毛不差 我果然是天才啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.02,0:06:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么帐簿在哪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.86,0:06:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望望美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.10,0:06:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东原望望美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动PBE时不可或缺的人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.23,0:06:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然军队跟小孩的组合很怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.17,0:06:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的存在却是5121部队的润滑剂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.04,0:06:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水厚志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.48,0:06:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HWT双人座机型中 负责操纵系统的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.55,0:07:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常生活虽然优柔寡断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在战场上关于双人座机型的操纵已有心得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.62,0:07:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟芝村舞的默契也有进步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.69,0:07:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最近看来训练成效不佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人在意的是芝村舞的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.51,0:07:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然跟部队成员相处比较好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.01,0:07:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但偶而会看到她表情哀愁 或是在想些心事的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论如何 这是个大问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中有股阴霾挥散不去对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.66,0:07:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次跟我约会喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恋爱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是小舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别隐瞒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟你讨论的我真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.18,0:08:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是害怕失败吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.95,0:08:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事应该做了再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.19,0:08:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你在烦恼什么 人生很多事情都来自经验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.19,0:08:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着踏出步伐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着踏出步伐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.14,0:08:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.54,0:08:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以进来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 不也是你自己的房间吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.91,0:08:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.78,0:08:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以问一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.05,0:08:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.16,0:08:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是 天气好的话也干得快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.43,0:08:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.66,0:08:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做模型 看就知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.80,0:09:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你喜欢模型啊 真是不错的兴趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兴趣是园艺喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.04,0:09:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时期牵牛花很棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是蓝色的 真的很漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.08,0:09:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么有点怪怪的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.59,0:09:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 像这么自然就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.19,0:09:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事应该做了再说 原来是这种涵意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？到底是啥啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 泷川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.50,0:09:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我抓到要领了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.31,0:09:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我无可取代的好友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该已经接吻了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞最近都若有所思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.85,0:09:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定在去年的圣诞节就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道已经那个了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人不好意思呢～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.73,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那个」是什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到「那个」就是那个啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要继续说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.37,0:10:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 在困境中萌芽的爱情 据说都不会长久呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.61,0:10:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别泼冷水啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.37,0:10:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该温暖地守护年轻男女的既成事实啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是既成事实吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既成事实是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不说明也没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.63,0:10:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过速水跟芝村配对的话 那就是金龟婿的女生版呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.87,0:10:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金龟婿是什么意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.80,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我跟远坂结婚 就等于是嫁给金龟婿喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边真正喜欢的是远坂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是举例啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小志要嫁给小舞吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有些不一样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就当成是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.43,0:11:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为“既成的事实” 所以成为小志的金龟婿好棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在乱教小孩子什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.48,0:11:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况那种人不是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.55,0:11:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事随便又懦弱闷骚 根本就是优柔寡断的范本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.42,0:11:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算全世界剩下他一个男的 我也不会多看他一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.86,0:11:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是因为工作 我根本不会跟他进驾驶舱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没起步就踩空了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.36,0:12:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是来关心长岭女高的资料吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.26,0:12:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前不是还想追芝村吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做事是往前看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有注意他们两人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然 训练数值一直在下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只会对数字有兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.18,0:13:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没发觉他们最近特意疏远吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.65,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是被这种无聊感情所困啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.65,0:13:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.65,0:13:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场上只需要友情 不是爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.06,0:13:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能分别爱情跟友情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.43,0:13:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在对你也只有友情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别吵了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.68,0:13:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用我的方法来做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我说不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.83,0:13:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为任务以外的事情而分心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招致自己遭遇危险是愚蠢至极
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务以外？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.11,0:14:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听清楚了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.85,0:14:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天接受训练 跟搭档培养默契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.85,0:14:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此共同努力的话 所有事情都可以顺心如意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.12,0:14:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.86,0:14:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要作好驾驶员的工作就行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要工作顺利的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会解决你所有的烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要摆出这么可怕的表惰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我叫我来这的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.39,0:15:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从以前就觉得你很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.63,0:15:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是开什么玩笑？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟壬生屋一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.31,0:15:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叫着「真是不纯洁」 而且愤怒得满脸通红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.71,0:15:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨呢 其实不会不纯洁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕会后悔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.82,0:15:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时连后悔都没办法喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己坦诚一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是要说这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我抓到要领了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.58,0:15:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.59,0:16:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些话想跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.64,0:16:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.98,0:16:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己坦诚一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于我们的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天起工作也要加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.49,0:16:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说的就是这些吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.48,0:17:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残弹数0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.08,0:17:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击坠率55%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的数值一直在下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.72,0:17:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我的建言完全没有成效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.82,0:17:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村舞努力要无视于速水厚志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.66,0:17:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那番话她没听进去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实一点不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说舞跟速水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.84,0:18:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是无法理解啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.61,0:18:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟芝村舞就是那样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.65,0:18:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那由男方主动不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过速水也是个小呆瓜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的看不下去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.86,0:18:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来揭发真相吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.14,0:18:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那照例是一个月的点心\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(恋爱进展大预测)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下注下注！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道选什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姊你怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.15,0:18:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 田边你觉得是哪边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.69,0:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这次也有自信喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.72,0:18:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啦 快说快说～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赌的就是这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.58,0:19:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望望美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.75,0:19:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.59,0:19:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.59,0:19:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美今天想要吃炸虾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-炸虾？\N-因为我喜欢吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要吃好多好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.89,0:19:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞刚刚在做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难得呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.96,0:20:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为看到的老是那些人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.63,0:20:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚去哪边呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.74,0:20:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜拳又输啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.81,0:20:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小志也一起牵手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是说不行啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.11,0:20:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一、二…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.52,0:21:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5121部队的运作应算顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使多少有些问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.20,0:21:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间终究会解决一切的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.12,0:21:47.56,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}最重要的心情 总是过于接近无法传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.07,0:22:00.07,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}擦肩而过时的悲伤 在我的内心紧紧纠结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.25,0:22:05.69,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}雨过天睛 光珠般的雨滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.29,0:22:11.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}我将其收集起来 藉以思念你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.43,0:22:19.39,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}没人知道我将前往何处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.70,0:22:25.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}只有明日的风描绘着我的轨迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.17,0:22:31.61,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}随着时代变动的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.88,0:22:37.61,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}即使迷失在困惑里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.95,0:22:43.91,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}也要抱紧这相遇的奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.39,0:22:54.16,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}走吧 一同前去
